basic.description:
{Basic Luck}

Increases the Luck of all hero's creatures by 1, improving their chance to deal double damage with lucky strikes.

Positive Luck can grant or improve selected chance-based creature abilities. Negative Luck can reduce some existing abilities.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Luck}

Increases the Luck of all hero's creatures by 2, improving their chance to deal double damage with lucky strikes.

Positive Luck can grant or improve selected chance-based creature abilities. Negative Luck can reduce some existing abilities.

